title: Miriel's Enchanted Mystery - NEW Time Management Game
description:
No Need For Patches Or Serials Just Run Installer And Enjoy The Game!

Join Miriel as she once again travels the world opening shops and using her magic to help sell tasty goods. This time, though, everything is
not as it seems! A mysterious artifact has come into her possession that leads her down a path of folklore, intrigue and ancient power. It's going to take a lot of work to save the world and Miriel needs your help!
